social_posts.post_text: Colors that become eye candy.

🍭🍬Releasing Saturday on the website from my personal collection. I had enough vintage towels to make 2 of these jackets and I already sold one, but was holding on this one for me. I’m ready..Someone is really going to love this pastel rainbow checker vintage towel jacket!

🆕A fresh batch of really special vintage pieces dropping on the website today at 6pm pst! 1960/70s hand blocked cotton a-line maxi or dress. 1960s rust colored suede leather hand bag. Artisan reversible open jacket mixed media painted leather with silk, patchwork and gold metallic vein cotton gauze. Sweet light 90s cotton denim eyelet boho cropped top. Vintage Banana Republic floral muted turquoise button down.
Looks of a new batch of curated vintage dropping on the website at 6pm pst. Size reference: 5’8” usually between m/l or Size 10.
🍊🍊It’s been a while..Here to share I’m releasing this 70s Orange Dream towel jacket tomorrow at 9am pst on the website! Best for up to a medium.

🌿🥑🦖 How does this beauty play on your eyes?! This is worth reading! Everything except custom on the website is on sale up until this Friday! Use Promo Code: SUMMER1. These vintage poppy themed towels and the colors of a deeper forest green, bright lime and creamy white, oh myyy.. Releasing Saturday on the website at 9am pst! Best for Medium.

🦖🌸Um.. Why were the 70s so good with colors and patterns. Imagine these original towels of hot pink and avocado green in a bathroom!! This one is releasing Saturday at 9am pst. Although, everything except custom is currently on sale until Friday! Use promo code: SUMMER1 at checkout!

🤩🤩Releasing this Y S L vintage upcycled towel jacket with the best geometric details on Saturday on the website at 9am pst. These are buttery soft!! Btw, there is a current SALE on mostly everything except custom going on now until Friday. Use promo code: SUMMER1 at checkout!
🆕🆕Lots of fresh new vintage towel tops releasing Saturday!

🐚🐚🐚**LAST DAY OF WEBSITE SALE! See my stories for the promo code!**From my personal collection and releasing on Saturday! I had one of these before and it sold instantly. I finally decided I can share now this one with you all! Someone is going to get lucky! Best for a M/L!
Let’s see what these towel tops look like on. This batch is releasing tomorrow on the website at 9am pst!
Beautiful vintage powder blue with the best paisley design details. All new items on the website right now!

😍😍😍Did you know these vintage towel mini skirts look amazing on their own BUT also with tights when the weather transitions?! Last batch of mini skirts releasing this Saturday! Size range between 6-10 us in this batch!
🌿🍃🌱the green monochromatic tones of these vintage towels into this open face jacket is 👩‍🍳😘! Releasing Saturday with the towel mini skirts!
🍁Starting up some pumpkin spice.. fresh batch of upcycled vintage towel mini skirts and a few vintage gem studded berets on the website!
🧡❤️💜🖤These colors and the chunkiness of the plaid! Vintage 70s mohair weaved quilt in to an amazing oversized open face jacket.. TBA on the release date!
Sharing and showing all the new vintage and some existing pieces with you all!

🍁🍂☕️🎃Just some of the latest vintage that is perfect for the new fall season releasing on the website this Wednesday at 3pm pst! Brands like Missoni, Bottega Veneta, Ralph Lauren, Dooney & Burke and Bergdorf Goodman!!
🖤💜🩷❤️Vintage Mohair cardigan jacket releasing Wednesday at 3pm pst on the website!

🧡💛🍂Just several amazing vintage towel upcycled jackets that are available on the website! Perfect color palette for the new season!!

Playing around this morning with vintage scarves. Silky little halters are perfect under something leather..

Several vintage southwest wool coats, buttery soft red leather jacket, a black label Ralph Lauren silver metallic cardigan, an Italian made cream stitched Y2K vest and Neiman Marcus mesh maxi dress. Beautiful patterns, striking colors and classic clean lines. What always attract my eye!
